<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink317">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>cūḻkam vammō tōḻipāḻ paṭṭup</l>
<l>paitaṟa venta pālai veṅkāṭ</l>
<l>ṭaruñcura miṟantōr tēettuc</l>
<l>ceṉṟa neñcam nīṭiya poruḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Come [here], friend! Let’s think about the reason,</l>
  <l>[why my] heart that is gone after the one who traversed</l>
    <l>the difficult desert in the heated wilderness,</l>
      <l>where Palai trees are ruined and their green [leaves] are entirely parched,</l> 
      <l rend="indent9">is delayed.</l>
</lg>

    </div>
